mutant: m018_commit_rev_dropped
target: internal/ingest/live/events.go
failure-mode: |
  In convertCommit (the MAIN live #commit path), the Rev field is dropped
  (set to ""). Models forgetting to copy a field on the hot path. Companion
  to m014, which mutated the resync fallback that simulator traffic never
  takes.
expected-detection: |
  CheckInvariants tracks per-DID rev monotonicity and Compare checks rev when
  both sides populate it; an empty rev should surface as a regression or
  mismatch. Default tier.
expected-tier: default
tiers: default,stress

